title: Garry Winogrand Dog in Central Park Holiday Cards
description:
A dog takes a snowy gallop through Central Park in the picturesque winter wonderland of Dog in Central Park, New York City, captured by acclaimed photographer Garry Winogrand (American, 1928–1984). "Season's Greetings" in red ink.

5 in. x 7 in.

Box of 20 individual cards
